<span font_family="monospace">
<span foreground="#ffb86c" weight="bold">󰣇  ESSENTIALS</span>
Help / Command Finder    <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+?</span>
Toggle Cheatsheet        <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+/</span>
Terminal                 <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Return</span>
Floating Terminal        <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Shift+Return</span>
App Launcher             <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+D</span>
Emoji Picker             <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+.</span>
Window Switcher          <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+P</span>
Kill Window              <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Shift+Q</span>
Kill App (all windows)   <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Ctrl+Shift+Q</span>
Lock Screen              <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+X</span>
Reload Config            <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Shift+C</span>
Toggle Waybar            <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Shift+B</span>
Theme Selector           <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+T</span>
Voice Dictation          <span foreground="#8be9fd">Ctrl+Shift+Space</span>
Claude Desktop           <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Ctrl+Space</span>

<span foreground="#50fa7b" weight="bold">󰖯  WINDOW LAYOUTS</span>
Stacking Mode            <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+S</span>
Tabbed Mode              <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+W</span>
Tiled / Toggle Split     <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+E</span>
Split Horizontal         <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+B</span>
Split Vertical           <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+V</span>
Toggle Floating          <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Shift+Space</span>
Focus Float ↔ Tile       <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Space</span>
Toggle Fullscreen        <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+F</span>
Global Fullscreen        <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Shift+F</span>
Focus Parent             <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+A</span>

<span foreground="#bd93f9" weight="bold">  NAVIGATION</span>
Focus L/D/U/R            <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+H/J/K/L  or  Mod+←↓↑→</span>
Move Window              <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Shift+H/J/K/L  or  Mod+Shift+←↓↑→</span>
Move Workspace           <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Alt+←↓↑→</span>
Last Used Window         <span foreground="#8be9fd">Alt+Tab</span>
Window Switcher (swayr)  <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+P</span>
Last Workspace           <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Tab</span>

<span foreground="#f1fa8c" weight="bold">  WORKSPACES</span>
Switch to 1–10           <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+1–0</span>
Move window to 1–10      <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Shift+1–0</span>
New Workspace            <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+N</span>
Move to new ws           <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Shift+N</span>
Move + switch to new ws  <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Shift+M</span>
Launcher in new ws       <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Shift+D</span>

<span foreground="#ff79c6" weight="bold">󱡂  MODES</span>
Screenshot Mode          <span foreground="#8be9fd">Print</span>
Recording Mode           <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Shift+R</span>
Stop Recording           <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Escape</span>
Resize Mode              <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+R</span>
Swap Mode                <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Ctrl+W</span>
Power Menu               <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Shift+E</span>

<span foreground="#ff5555" weight="bold">  SCRATCHPAD</span>
Send to Scratchpad       <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+Shift+-</span>
Show Scratchpad          <span foreground="#8be9fd">Mod+-</span>
</span>
